---
const currentlyLearning = ['Game Development', 'Piano']
---

<section
  id='hero'
  class='min-h-screen bg-parchment flex flex-col pt-14 relative overflow-hidden'
>
  <div
    class='absolute top-10 right-0 w-72 h-72 halftone rounded-full border-brutal translate-x-1/3 opacity-60 pointer-events-none'
    aria-hidden='true'
  ></div>

  <div class='absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-4 bg-charcoal pointer-events-none' aria-hidden='true'></div>

  <div
    class='absolute top-14 left-0 w-2 h-48 bg-red-accent pointer-events-none'
    aria-hidden='true'
  ></div>

  <div class='flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full px-8 md:px-16 py-16 pb-24'>
    <div class='flex items-center gap-4 mb-6'>
      <span class='w-12 h-px bg-charcoal'></span>
      <span class='font-display text-olive text-sm tracking-widest'>FRONTEND ENGINEER</span>
    </div>

    <div class='flex items-stretch gap-0'>
      <div class='flex-1 min-w-0'>
        <h1 class='font-display text-charcoal leading-none tracking-tight'>
          <span class='block text-[clamp(5rem,15vw,14rem)]'>JERI ツ</span>
          <span class='block text-[clamp(2rem,6vw,5.5rem)] text-olive mt-[-0.15em]'>SOFTWARE</span>
          <span class='block text-[clamp(2rem,6vw,5.5rem)] leading-none'>
            ENGINEER<span class='text-red-accent'>.</span>
          </span>
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class='hidden lg:flex flex-col justify-between border-l-brutal border-charcoal ml-10 pl-10 shrink-0 w-64 xl:w-80 py-1'>
        <div>
          <div class='flex gap-2 mb-6'>
            <span class='relative flex h-2 w-2 shrink-0 mt-px'>
              <span class='animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-red-accent opacity-75'></span>
              <span class='relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-red-accent'></span>
            </span>
            <span class='font-display text-xs text-red-accent tracking-widest leading-none'>CURRENTLY LEARNING</span>
          </div>

          <ul class='flex flex-col gap-0 border-t-brutal border-charcoal'>
            {currentlyLearning.map((item) => (
              <li class='font-display text-[clamp(1.25rem,2.5vw,1.75rem)] text-charcoal tracking-tight border-b-3 border-charcoal py-3 leading-none'>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p class='font-body text-xs text-charcoal/40 mt-6 leading-relaxed'>
          Things I'm actively digging into.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start max-w-2xl'>
      <p class='font-body text-charcoal/70 text-base leading-relaxed flex-1'>
        I like building things mostly software, occasionally something that breaks. When I'm not at the keyboard, I'm probably with my cat.
      </p>

      <div class='flex gap-3 shrink-0 items-end'>
        <div class='flex flex-col gap-3'>
          <a
            href='#projects'
            class='inline-block border-brutal bg-charcoal text-parchment font-display tracking-widest text-lg px-8 py-3 hover:bg-red-accent hover:border-red-accent transition-colors duration-150 shadow-brutal'
          >
            PROJECTS
          </a>
          <a
            href='#contact'
            class='inline-block border-brutal text-charcoal font-display tracking-widest text-lg px-8 py-3 hover:bg-charcoal hover:text-parchment transition-colors duration-150'
          >
            CONTACT
          </a>
        </div>
        <a
          href='/personal-site/blog'
          class='inline-block md:hidden border-brutal border-red-accent text-red-accent font-display tracking-widest text-lg px-8 py-3 hover:bg-red-accent hover:text-parchment transition-colors duration-150'
        >
          BLOG
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id='skills' class='mt-16 flex flex-wrap gap-0 border-t-brutal border-charcoal pt-6'>
      {['TypeScript', 'React', 'Next.js', 'Tailwind CSS', 'Styled-Components', 'GraphQL', 'Cypress', 'Playwright'].map((skill) => (
        <span class='font-body text-sm text-charcoal/70 border-r-brutal border-charcoal pr-4 mr-4 py-1 last:border-r-0'>
          {skill}
        </span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 opacity-50'>
    <span class='font-display text-xs text-charcoal tracking-widest'>SCROLL</span>
    <div class='w-px h-10 bg-charcoal animate-pulse'></div>
  </div>
</section>
